{"tid":2078470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"山西前首富24億資產 0.2折無人接","createTime":"2020-06-25T05:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T07:17:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d323862605ece4b8294faa521e6e54e537f315c","tid":2078470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200625/IQ2FCLTEF4JJ4WDABE7Y5RRYHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200625%2FIQ2FCLTEF4JJ4WDABE7Y5RRYHE%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=d60a62a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200625%2FIQ2FCLTEF4JJ4WDABE7Y5RRYHE%2F&h=086f0656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200625/IQ2FCLTEF4JJ4WDABE7Y5RRYHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n山西前首富24億資產 0.2折無人接<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zqK9dUcgxyhUvouwNTA8VvvUnYg=/190x137/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DWGLF5KP3GFKCSWISACK3AF3FI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzqK9dUcgxyhUvouwNTA8VvvUnYg%3D%2F190x137%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDWGLF5KP3GFKCSWISACK3AF3FI.gif&h=7c196af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李兆會曾大灑金錢迎娶女星車曉。<br />\n<br />\n前山西最大民企海鑫鋼鐵集團破產易名後，現齡38歲的前董事長李兆會名下五間公司總值22.35億元人民幣（下同，約24.5億港元）的應收賬款，上月起四度流拍，惟即使打了0.2折至6,000萬元（約6,580萬港元），仍未有人敢貿然接貨。<br />\n<br />\n阿里司法拍賣平台顯示，李兆會擁有旗下五間公司總值22億元應收賬款及股息債權，這批資產於本月9日被強行拍賣，惟估值只有1.24億元（約1.36億港元），且四度流標。拍賣行見狀將價格下調至6,000萬元，即原來價值的2.7%，仍無人問津。據報該筆資產看似值。。。。。。。。。。。。。。原因。內媒指出，李兆會曾十次被列為「全國失信被執行人名單」、「限制消費人員名單」，如今名下已無可供執行的財產。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先後迎娶兩女星<br />\n<br />\n李2003年接手亡。。。。。。。。。。。。。。產被法院查封與拍賣。他近年已不再公開露面，行蹤成謎。<br />\n<br />\n新浪新聞"},{"pid":"a464495d9377b501a52e1398366f87ed11937a8e","tid":2078470,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"10幾20年前既死債"},{"pid":"1ee480523a76cdf3da65653ba924028596d587a5","tid":2078470,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"老婆女星有無人接？"},{"pid":"6d7508a0c41bcf0862faf5b1090b2a1646c8c7ed","tid":2078470,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ee480523a76cdf3da65653ba924028596d587a5","tid":2078470,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"老婆女星有無人接？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"uh? used?"}]}